\n| Lars Emberg\n| N. Cederholm/Dante\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.danskfilmogteater.dk/teatertitler/aveny/paradis.htm |title= Paradis|website=danskfilmogteater.dk|accessdate=21 March 2017|language=Danish}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row| ''Lovestory''\n| Martin\n| [[Mungo Park (theatre)|Mungo Park]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kb.dk/images/billed/2010/okt/billeder/object209543/da/ |title= Lovestory|website=kb.dk|accessdate=21 March 2017|language=Danish}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2000\n!scope=row| ''Drengene i Skyggen ''\n| Christoffer\n| [[Betty Nansen Teatret|Betty Nansen Theater]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.b.dk/kultur/noren-stykke-forlaenges-igen|title= Nor\u00e9n-stykke forl\u00e6nges igen|website=b.dk|accessdate=21 March 2017|language=Danish}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2002\n!scope=row| ''[[Becket]]''\n| Becket\n| Gladsaxe Ny Teater\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.danskfilmogteater.dk/teatertitler/Gladsaxe/becket_2002.html |title= Becket|website=danskfilmogteater.dk|accessdate=21 March 2017|language=Danish}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2009\n!scope=row| '' \u00d8jeblikket''\n|\n| [[Betty Nansen Teatret|Betty Nansen Theater]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.danskfilmogteater.dk/teatertitler/betty_nansen/2000/ojeblikket_2009.html |title= \u00d8jeblikket|website=danskfilmogteater.dk|accessdate=21 March 2017|language=Danish}}</ref>\n|-\n|2020\n!scope=row| '' [[Macbeth]]''\n|Macbeth \n|[[Geffen Playhouse]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\":3\" />\n|}\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Award\n! scope=\"col\" | Category\n! scope=\"col\" | Work\n! scope=\"col\" | Result\n!{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n| 1994\n| [[Bodil Awards]]\n| [[Bodil Award for Best Actor in a Leading Role|Best Actor]]\n| ''[[Nightwatch (1994 film)|Nightwatch]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-